title: Boudewijn de Groot - De Fietstocht (Dutch Treat ^B073 HQ VBR)
description:
Boudewijn de Groot is the Bob Dylon and James Taylor from the Low Lands. 33 tracks are not enough to cover him. Fortunately a lot of old Hits sounded quite poor (Boudewijn does not want to sound like that). So I had to make some concessions. And that left some room for less known songs that are more pleasant to listen to.. Enjoy,
